3 days until I’m with my family in Miami ☀️Paying extra attention to my skincare routine the next few days so I’m ready to go for the plane and warmer temperatures. I’ve worked with @vichyusa for a while now, and they have a new product, Mineral 89 Eyes, which I’ve been using  to help hydrate my skin between trips. If you’re looking for new eye cream, here’s what makes this one stand out— It’s formulated with natural origin hyaluronic acid which and their highest concentration of thermal water that is rich in 15 minerals. It also has pure caffeine to brighten the appearance of dark circles and depuff any undereye bags. #ad #purityispotency

Today was my turn to go to Ruby’s school and read to her class. When we sat down in front her friends and teachers, she took the book from me and said mommy, I’d like to read to the class instead. She read the entire book from start to finish based on memory and I’ve never been more proud of my baby. This was such a special moment. Even the teachers said they could have called in sick today because ruby was so amazing at being teacher and calling out to each classmate at the end and asking them to share their favorite part of the book. If someone didn’t have an answer she told them she’d give them a few minutes and come back to them. Also the leg cross 😭❤️
